"I had no idea I\xe2\x80\x99d use this as much as I do. This Snap-on Video Inspection Scope has paid for itself a hundred times over. I use it to inspect gears through the fill/drain holes, use like a mechanics mirror looking behind an obstacle or blind spot, and most recently I used it to verify the condition of a used engine before installing it into a customers Jeep. Luckily I had this in the tool box. I was able to remove the coil pack and spark plug and look down through the spark plug hole, discovering the cylinder walls are scored so badly this engine is junk. This scope has a 2.5\xe2\x80\x9d color screen, stores 30 images onboard, has zoom, image rotation, adjustable brightness on the light, etc. A definite must have!"
